channel.title: GeForce 667 Recruiting!
channel.description:
Hello, I am Katastrphy Owner of GeForce Project. I am recruiting a team for my rsps. Currently looking for someone with experience with java, mysql and coding in 667+. Currently using rscali v2 as base. i have a vps.
I am Also looking for someone that can do client sided also.
The map data is very messed up in some areas. I'm also hoping to learn a bit of java from this myself. I don't like older revisions and love full screen which is why i'm not starting with 317. Plus there isn't allot of good 667+ out there.
If you're interested please contact me via skype: dmxrb89
